reviewText: I love the history and nostalgia.  I grew up in the eighties as a kid and then the nineties as a teenager.  It was nice seeing the changes each decade brought and reveal in my childhood again.  I just wish their was one for the nineties and the oughts.
Every was good. Product, shipping and price
Gave as a gift. Recipient loves it. Would recommend.
Well done, enjoyed each DVD very much.

Great set of historical references for each decade. I loved all of them. Fun and nostalgic. Lots of content. Full movies, TV episodes, commercials and informative information. Highly recommended for the history buff or pop culture buff.
Love these! I sent them out this year for birthdays!
